          <h2> When did you first hear about Inkscape?
I first heard about inkscape when my friend used it to make an SVG image for a club project he was working on.

What kind of drawings do you create with Inkscape?
I have tried inkscape for creating simple shapes like figure. Not an artwork though.

Describe your participation in our community (e.g. uploaded drawings, tutorials, bug reports, communication via mailing lists or IRC).
I have fixed some bugs on the inkscape website. Apart from that, I have contacted the web admin whenever necessary or in doubt over mailing list and IRC.

Describe your contributions to the Inkscape development (e.g. bug fixes, translations, packaging, testing).
I have added jquery validation in the resource form of the inkscape-web repository. Now the data,size of the image and link is validated on the front end instead of the previous back end validation for a trouble free experience for the user. If they chose a much bigger file than their limit or forgot to fill some required fields, a suitable error will be displayed to the user near the error field.

In exactly two sentences, why should we pick YOU?
Well, I have all of the skills and experience that is needed for this project. I am reliable and have complete dedication and passion about my work, my responsibilities are my first priorities.

What is your name, email address, and irc nickname?
Name: Rohit Lodha
Personal Email: rohit.lodhartg@gmail.com
University Email: f2015040@pilani.bits-pilani.ac.in
Freenode irc: rtgdk_ or rohitrtg( when i use freenode through mobile)

Describe any plans you have for the summer in addition to GSoC (classes, thesis, job, vacation, etc.).
Our college provide a practice school internship for sophomores where they are placed in any organisation( research institute,startup,NGOs, etc.) across India during the summer . So, I will have my internship during the 2 month period(June-July) but I am sure that it will not have any effect on my work and will manage my time accordingly.

